Detailed Description

IMSRGravity is a wrapper class for an NSDictionary, which contains the gravitational attraction at the surface of several celestial bodies, such as Earth, Moon and Jupiter. The NSDictionary is initialized from a property list (Gravity.plist).

Gravity is always negative. The units are meters/sec2.
